item.g:description:
Used in the work:
- fragments of Sergei Sparis’ sneakers torn by riot police, an activist of Narodnaya Hramada on June 21, 2019, during a picket;
- clippings of collages glued together by Nikolai Dedok while in solitary confinement, a political prisoner sentenced in 2011 to 4.5 years in prison in the "anarchist case";
- the shirt sleeves, holding on to which, the valiant fighters captured Maxim Kovalev, one of the founders of the Student Block movement, on March 25, 2017 during mass protests in the cult temporary detention center on Akrestsin Street.
